Santander in Talks With Funds to Sell Property, Expansion Says

-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 
2011-10-18T05:25:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/santander-in-talks-with-funds-to-sell-property-expansion-says.html
Banco Santander SA (SAN)  is in talks with
two international funds to sell 3 billion euros ($4.1 billion)
worth of property assets,  Expansion  reported, citing
unidentified people with knowledge of the talks.  The portfolio comprises 60 percent homes, 20 percent land
and 20 percent offices and will be sold at a discount of more
than 50 percent, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sharon Smyth in Madrid at 
 ssmyth2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Blackman at 
 ablackman@bloomberg.net  